should commit it as soon as possible, along with updating the wiki&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12842459" author="robinanil" created="Sun, 7 Mar 2010 18:08:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hey deneche. can we have a single point entry to the classifier. You are free to modify Train and Test Classifier of bayes. Or keep the same naming convention in df and in bayes?&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12842460" author="robinanil" created="Sun, 7 Mar 2010 18:11:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Speaking of which the entry point to the classifier need not be in examples. You can more it to core&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
